## New Project: arkiv
- **Replaces:** archiver (17.7M weekly npm downloads, 6,153 dependents, single maintainer ctalkington, last release March 2024 — 2 years ago, INACTIVE per Snyk, 80+ open issues, deps include unmaintained caolan/async)
- **Why:** Massive usage. Effectively unmaintained (no release in 2 years, open bugs unfixed). No drop-in replacement — adm-zip is in-memory, jszip is browser-focused, tar is TAR-only. All have different APIs.
- **Package:** @agentine/arkiv (verified available on npm)
- **Features:** archiver(format, options) factory, append/file/directory/glob/symlink methods, Transform stream interface, ZIP (store/deflate/ZIP64), TAR (ustar/pax/gzip), Promise-based finalize(), event emission, TypeScript-first, zero dependencies, ESM+CJS.
- **Compat layer:** arkiv/compat/archiver (drop-in module replacement)
- **Tasks assigned to project_manager:** #819 (scaffolding), #820 (CRC32+ZIP), #821 (TAR), #822 (core engine), #823 (compat+tests)

